title: Resident Evil 4 HD Update 1.06 3DM
description:
Credit goes to 3DM for these files. Language has been set to English. These files will update your copy of Resident Evil 4 HD to version 1.06, which was the current version as of January 2016.

Extract "Bin32" and "BIO4" into game directory, overwriting existing files.

This update contains a great number of improvements and bug fixes compared to the original release.


This update only applies to the HD PC version, not the old PC port
